Interface Request

All Superinterfaces:
BaseRequest, DimensionsArObject, DimensionsLcObject, DimensionsObject
public interface Request
extends BaseRequest, DimensionsLcObject

Represent a Dimensions request with optional attribute values and relationships populated into its cache.

actionTo

DimensionsResult actionTo(java.lang.String status,
                          boolean actionCheck,
                          boolean closureCheck)
Action a request to the given state.

Parameters:
status - Specifies the new state to be given to the request
actionCheck - Indicates that Dimensions is to check whether the specified request can be either actioned to the specified state or the next normal state if state is not specified, while conforming to the current rules.
closureCheck - Indicates that Dimensions is to check whether the specified request can be actioned to the final state in its normal lifecycle, while conforming to the current rules.
Returns:
DimensionsResult The result of the operation

delegateForReplicationTo

DimensionsResult delegateForReplicationTo(java.lang.String site,
                                          java.lang.String mode,
                                          boolean delegateItems)
Delegates a role to a replication site rather than a specific user.

Parameters:
site - allows the request to be delegated to a replication site rather than a specific user.
mode - Add (default) user(s) are to have this role for this request in addition to those who already have it., Replace user(s) are to have this role for this request instead of those who already have it. Delete user(s) are to be removed from the list of users who have this role for this request.
delegateItems - True if the current assignment shall be replaced
Returns:
DimensionsResult

delegateTo

DimensionsResult delegateTo(java.util.List users,
                            java.lang.String role,
                            java.lang.String capability,
                            java.lang.String mode,
                            boolean delegateItems)
Delegates a role on this request to a set of users.

Parameters:
users - the set of users to delegate the role to.
role - the name of the role definition to delegate.
capability - the capability flags to delegate with ("P" for Primary, "S" for Secondary (default) or "L" for Leader).
mode - "Add" (default) user(s) are to have this role for this request in addition to those who already have it. "Replace" user(s) are to have this role for this request instead of those who already have it. "Delete" user(s) are to be removed from the list of users who have this role for this request.
delegateItems - True if the current assignment shall be replaced
Returns:
DimensionsResult

deploy

@Deprecated
DimensionsResult deploy(java.lang.String stage,
                                   java.lang.String comment,
                                   boolean traverseChildren)
Deprecated. As of CM 12.1, use promote(String, String, boolean) or demote(String, String, boolean) instead.

Deploys a request to the given stage using CM 2009 R2 stage deployment. Promotion or demotion to a stage has replaced stage deployment as of CM 12.1 or later.

Parameters:
stage - The target stage to deploy to.
comment - The comment applied to the stage deployment.
traverseChildren - Set this to true if dependent child requests should be deployed to the stage as well.
Returns:
DimensionsResult The result of the operation.
